fields.name: Description & Benefits
fields.value:
Beets are widely known for boosting nitric oxide which in turn helps circulation, blood vessel health & cardio support. Our blend is further fortified with BCAA, L Arginine, L Carnitine and resveratrol for maximum health benefits, pre/post workout energy, endurance & stamina.

Includes All The Nutrients In Beetroot Including Fiber, Potassium, Manganese, Vitamin C, Zinc, Copper, And Iron. Our Beets Contain Polyphenols And Betalains, Which Are Natural Antioxidants To Neutralize Dangerous Free Radicals In The Body.
